ayman, one who delivered beer and wine in bulk to customers; in some instances the surname may have been acquired in either of these senses. This surname is also found France (Alsace and Lorraine) and Poland. Compare   Schroder  ."]}]},{"name":"Gesche","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of American Family Names © Patrick Hanks 2003, 2006.","meanings":["German (also <b>Gösche</b>): variant of   Gosch  ."],"variants":[{"name":"Gosch","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  German Hans, Claus, Erwin, Guenther, Heinz, Helmut, Kurt.","North German (also <b>Gösch</b>): from a shortened form of the personal name <b>Godschalk</b>, Low German form of   Gottschalk  .","South German (Bavaria and Austria): nickname from <i>Gosche(n)</i> ‘mouth’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Gesche Schroder was born in 1540, in Saxony, Germany. She married Severus Hanses Schroder in 1560. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died in 1590, at the age of 50."},"et":{"1540–1590":"1540–1590","1540–1592":"1540–1592","1560–1636":"1560–1636","1540":"1540","1560":"1560","1592":"1592","1590":"1590","1636":"1636","Altenfeld, Winterberg, Hochsauerlandkreis, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Deutschland":"Altenfeld, Winterberg, Hochsauerlandkreis, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Saksamaa","Enanyglesdorf, Leipsig, Saxony, Germany":"Sachsen, Saksamaa"},"fi":{"1540–1590":"1540–1590","1540–1592":"1540–1592","1560–1636":"1560–1636","1540":"1540","1560":"1560","1592":"1592","1590":"1590","1636":"1636","Altenfeld, Winterberg, Hochsauerlandkreis, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Deutschland":"Altenfeld, Winterberg, Hochsauerlandkreis, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Saksa","Enanyglesdorf, Leipsig, Saxony, Germany":"Sachsen, Saksa"},"fr":{"1540–1590":"1540–1590","1540–1592":"1540–1592","1560–1636":"1560–1636","1540":"1540","1560":"1560","1592":"1592","1590":"1590","1636":"1636","Altenfeld, Winterberg, Hochsauerlandkreis, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Deutschland":"Altenfeld, Winterberg, Hochsauerlandkreis, Nordrhein-Westfalen, Allemagne","Enanyglesdorf, Leipsig